    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>into wedges</p><p>Top, tail and slice the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into rounds</p>",
      "order": 1,
