            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>red onion wedges</strong> and <strong>courgette rounds</strong> to 1<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2] </span>baking tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Sprinkle over<strong> </strong>the<strong> ras el hanout</strong>,<strong> </strong>the<strong> </strong>juice of<strong> </strong>1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give it a good mix up until everything is coated</p>",
